sentences.english: My name is Salmon, like the fish. First name, Susie.

sentences.english: Thee falls upstream are full of salmons.
sentences.chinese: 该瀑布上游有许多大马哈鱼。

sentences.english: Sockeye salmon may use their ultraviolet perception to see food.
sentences.chinese: 红大马哈鱼能利用紫外线的穿透力看见食物。

sentences.english: Soon after spawning, the adult Pacific salmon will expire.
sentences.chinese: 产卵之后，大马哈鱼很快也就寿终正寝了。
